 3673}, {\"ngram\": \"Business\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3685}, {\"ngram\": \"Management\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In boxing, you do not have to come from a background where you are disobedient in school and can not pay attention, because I wasn't that kind of person.\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"a background\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3818}, {\"ngram\": \"that kind\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes you have got to grit your teeth and fight but I am trying to push out the message that as long as you are dedicated and focused, you can achieve great things in this sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 4041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your teeth\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3899}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 3949}, {\"ngram\": \"great things\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4025}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie has an evangelical belief in keeping things simple, devoting every waking thought to how he might improve his ring craft.\", \"from\": 4043, \"to\": 4169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an evangelical belief\", \"from\": 4052, \"to\": 4073}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4091}, {\"ngram\": \"every waking thought\", \"from\": 4109, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"his ring craft\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have three big square meals every day with some protein shakes in between,\\\" said Orie, who is supported by supermarket Aldi.\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4293, \"end\": 4297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, 